  <brief_title>Pre-operative Withdrawal of Aspirin in Laparoscopic Inguinal Hernia Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial on Pre-operative Withdrawal Versus no Withdrawal of Aspirin in Laparoscopic Inguinal Hernia Repair</official_title>
  <sponsors>
